Depends: iproute2, util-linux, {{ DEPS }}
Description: seed the DaemonCores VE firewall config into pmxcfs on first boot
 A oneshot service that installs the cluster-wide and per-node firewall
 templates into the Proxmox VE cluster filesystem (/etc/pve) once pmxcfs has
 mounted it.
 .
 The templates are shipped under /usr/share on purpose: /etc/pve is a FUSE
 mountpoint owned by pmxcfs, and any file placed there in the image makes the
 mount fail ("fuse_mount error: File exists"), which cascades into every PVE
 service failing. This service copies them in after the mount is up, resolving
 the local management network for the cluster IPSET.
